default_style.name: TEMPERATURASMINENERO2030
default_style.sld_body:
b'<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<StyledLayerDescriptor xmlns="http://www.opengis.net/sld" xmlns:gml="http://www.opengis.net/gml" version="1.0.0" xmlns:sld="http://www.opengis.net/sld" xmlns:ogc="http://www.opengis.net/ogc">
  <UserLayer>
    <sld:LayerFeatureConstraints>
      <sld:FeatureTypeConstraint/>
    </sld:LayerFeatureConstraints>
    <sld:UserStyle>
      <sld:Name>TEMPERATURASMINENERO2030</sld:Name>
      <sld:FeatureTypeStyle>
        <sld:Rule>
          <sld:RasterSymbolizer>
            <sld:ChannelSelection>
              <sld:GrayChannel>
                <sld:SourceChannelName>1</sld:SourceChannelName>
              </sld:GrayChannel>

            <sld:ColorMap type="intervals">
              <sld:ColorMapEntry color="#132e58" quantity="-49" label="<= -4.90"/>

              <sld:ColorMapEntry color="#127ebd" quantity="-1" label="-3.19 - -1.00"/>
              <sld:ColorMapEntry color="#55c5d3" quantity="5" label="-0.09 - 0.5"/>
              <sld:ColorMapEntry color="#aefdf4" quantity="17" label="0.51 - 1.70"/>
              <sld:ColorMapEntry color="#c7fd7e" quantity="40" label="1.71 - 4.00"/>
              <sld:ColorMapEntry color="#83e611" quantity="50" label="4.01 - 5.00"/>
              <sld:ColorMapEntry color="#6baa14" quantity="83" label="5.01 - 8.30"/>
              <sld:ColorMapEntry color="#517317" quantity="120" label="8.31 - 12.00"/>
              <sld:ColorMapEntry color="#337208" quantity="187" label="12.01 - 18.70"/>
            </sld:ColorMap>
          </sld:RasterSymbolizer>
        </sld:Rule>
      </sld:FeatureTypeStyle>
    </sld:UserStyle>
  </UserLayer>
</StyledLayerDescriptor>
'

default_style.name: KM
default_style.sld_body:
b'
<StyledLayerDescriptor version="1.0.0" xmlns="http://www.opengis.net/sld" xmlns:ogc="http://www.opengis.net/ogc"
  xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
  xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.opengis.net/sld http://schemas.opengis.net/sld/1.0.0/StyledLayerDescriptor.xsd">
  <NamedLayer>
    <Name>KM</Name>
    <UserStyle>
    <Name>KM</Name>
    <Title>KM</Title>
      <FeatureTypeStyle>
        <Rule>

<PointSymbolizer>
  <Graphic>
    <Mark>
      <WellKnownName>x</WellKnownName>
      <Fill>
        <CssParameter name="fill">#000088</CssParameter>
      </Fill>
      <Stroke>
        <CssParameter name="stroke">#bbbbff</CssParameter>
      </Stroke>
    </Mark>
    <Size>10</Size>
  </Graphic>
</PointSymbolizer>

        </Rule>
      </FeatureTypeStyle>
    </UserStyle>
  </NamedLayer>
</StyledLayerDescriptor>
'
